Package: myergm
Title: Implementing a Toy ERGM from Scratch in R
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Shota",
           family = "Komatsu",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "first.last@example.com",
           comment = c(ORCID = "YOUR-ORCID-ID"))
Description: The myergm package tries to estimate the edges and triangle parameters 
from scratch as much as possible. 
If you carefully look at the source code, you will realize that myergm implements 
an MPLE using the ergm package. This is totally attributed to the author's laziness.
